OL,3,CWhat is in the asylum seeker overhaul
OL,4,Cand why is it inspired by Denmark's
OL,5,Claws?
OL,7,FThe home secretary is set to announce
OL,8,Fsweeping reforms to the UK's asylum
OL,9,Fsystem, which have largely been
OL,10,Fmodelled on Denmark's tough laws.
OL,12,FShabana Mahmood will overhaul of the
OL,13,Fway Britain grants sanctuary to those
OL,14,Ffleeing conflict and hardship abroad,
OL,15,Fin a statement in the House of Commons
OL,16,Fon Monday.
OL,18,FThe reforms are aimed at making
OL,19,FBritain a less attractive destination
OL,20,Ffor illegal migrants and making it
OL,21,Feasier to remove them from the UK.
