OL,3,CWhat is in the asylum seeker overhaul
OL,4,Cand why is it inspired by Denmark's
OL,5,Claws?
OL,7,FShe has cited Denmark as an
OL,8,Finspiration for the reforms, which
OL,9,Fhave reduced its inflow of asylum
OL,10,Fseekers to its lowest level in 40
OL,11,Fyears.
OL,13,FDenmark has heavily reformed its
OL,14,Fasylum system in recent years after
OL,15,Flarge inflows of refugees in the
OL,16,F2010s, mostly while ruled by a
OL,17,Fpolitical party ideologically similar
OL,18,Fto Labour.
