OL,3,CWhat is in the asylum seeker overhaul
OL,4,Cand why is it inspired by Denmark's
OL,5,Claws?
OL,7,FSenior Home Office officials were
OL,8,Fdispatched to Copenhagen to learn
OL,9,Fabout the country's asylum policy
OL,10,Fearlier this year.
OL,12,FWhat changes is the Government making?
OL,14,FMahmood will revoke the legal duty to
OL,15,Fprovide asylum-seeker support,
OL,16,Fintroduced in 2005 via EU law. This
OL,17,Fmeans housing and weekly allowances
OL,18,Fwill no longer be guaranteed for
OL,19,Fasylum seekers.
