OL,3,CWhat is in the asylum seeker overhaul
OL,4,Cand why is it inspired by Denmark's
OL,5,Claws?
OL,7,FThose who have a right to work in the
OL,8,FUK and can support themselves, but do
OL,9,Fnot, could also be denied housing and
OL,10,Fbenefits because of the change, as
OL,11,Fcould lawbreakers.
OL,13,FRefugee status will become temporary
OL,14,Fand subject to regular review.
OL,15,FRefugees will be removed as soon as
OL,16,Ftheir home countries are deemed safe.
OL,17,FThe wait for permanent settlement will
OL,18,Fbe quadrupled to 20 years.
