OL,3,CWhat is in the asylum seeker overhaul
OL,4,Cand why is it inspired by Denmark's
OL,5,Claws?
OL,7,FNew safe and legal routes to the UK
OL,8,Fwill be introduced as a way to cut
OL,9,Fdangerous journeys in small boats
OL,10,Facross the English Channel.
OL,12,FLocal communities will be able to
OL,13,Fsponsor individual refugees in a model
OL,14,Fsimilar to the Homes for Ukraine
OL,15,Fscheme, in which people hosted those
OL,16,Fin need in their homes.
