OL,3,CWhat is in the asylum seeker overhaul
OL,4,Cand why is it inspired by Denmark's
OL,5,Claws?
OL,7,FThe Danish government drastically
OL,8,Fchanged its migration system in
OL,9,Fresponse to a major influx of people
OL,10,Fthroughout the 2010s. As a result,
OL,11,Fasylum seekers can only get temporary
OL,12,Fresidence permits for one to two years.
OL,14,FResidency is subject to regular
OL,15,Freview, and can be revoked once a
OL,16,Frefugee's home country is deemed safe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
