OL,3,CWhat is in the asylum seeker overhaul
OL,4,Cand why is it inspired by Denmark's
OL,5,Claws?
OL,7,FRefugees are usually eligible for
OL,8,Fpermanent status after eight years,
OL,9,Fand in order to get it they must speak
OL,10,Ffluent Danish and are required to have
OL,11,Fhad a job for several years.
OL,13,FThere are also supplementary
OL,14,Frequirements, including "active
OL,15,Fcitizenship".
OL,17,FPeople refused asylum must live in
OL,18,F"departure centres", a basic standard
OL,19,Fof accommodation designed to
OL,20,Fincentivise a voluntary return home.
