OL,3,CWhat is in the asylum seeker overhaul
OL,4,Cand why is it inspired by Denmark's
OL,5,Claws?
OL,7,FFamily reunification is also subject
OL,8,Fto strict tests, including that both a
OL,9,Fsponsor and their partner must be over
OL,10,F24 years old, in a bid to prevent
OL,11,Fforced marriages.
OL,13,FA controversial policy known as the
OL,14,F"jewellery law" allows the Danish
OL,15,Fauthorities to confiscate asylum
OL,16,Fseekers' assets, including jewellery,
OL,17,Fto help fund the costs of their stay
OL,18,Fin Denmark. Assets of "special
OL,19,Fpersonal significance" should not be
OL,20,Ftaken.
