OL,3,CWhat is in the asylum seeker overhaul
OL,4,Cand why is it inspired by Denmark's
OL,5,Claws?
OL,7,FThe effect of Denmark's policies has
OL,8,Fbeen to reduce the number of asylum
OL,9,Fapplications to the lowest number in
OL,10,F40 years, and remove 95% of rejected
OL,11,Fasylum seekers.
OL,13,FIt has, however, been criticised by
OL,14,Fsome opponents as racist, and elements
OL,15,Fof it were previously found to have
OL,16,Fbreached human rights law.
OL,18,FThe Danish government is led by a
OL,19,Fpolitical party which has a philosophy
OL,20,Fsimilar to Britain's Labour Party.
