OL,3,CWhat is in the asylum seeker overhaul
OL,4,Cand why is it inspired by Denmark's
OL,5,Claws?
OL,7,FIt is seen as a model for the way a
OL,8,Fleft-leaning administration can roll
OL,9,Fout an immigration crackdown, placate
OL,10,Fvoters' concerns about migration, and
OL,11,Fdefeat political rivals.
